title: Trackmania² Lagoon
notes: Maniaplanet common files are currently duplicated using $WINEPREFIX, recommend sharing %ProgramData%\Maniaplanet & %USERPROFILE%\My Documents\Maniaplanet across all related products.

Game was downloaded via Stadium (All TM2 games can be downloaded like that), first 2 minutes of driving included a few lag spikes, but after that it runs like a charm. No noticeable faults in the editors (Map and skin). Skin from Steam Workshop are also perfectly loaded, with shadows, sounds, etc.
